1. *Uhvatio* sam loptu koju je bacio brat. (I caught the ball that my brother threw.)
2. Nisam mogao *uhvatiti* tramvaj, već sam morao čekati sljedeći. (I couldn't catch the tram, so I had to wait for the next one.)
3. Kada se zemljotres dogodio, ljudi su se trudili *uhvatiti* ravnotežu. (When the earthquake happened, people tried to maintain their balance.)
4. Želim *uhvatiti* taj vlak, pa se moram požuriti. (I want to catch that train, so I have to hurry.)
5. Možete li mi pomoći da *uhvatim* ovog psa koji bježi? (Can you help me catch this dog that is running away?)
6. Učiteljica me je uhvatila kako prepisujem na testu. (The teacher caught me cheating on the test.)
7. Kada sam vidio pauka, nisam se usudio *uhvatiti* ga golim rukama. (When I saw the spider, I didn't dare catch it with my bare hands.)
8. *Uhvati* me ako padnem! (Catch me if I fall!)